== About Me
I am a Postdoctoral Scholar at [http://www.stanford.edu Stanford University] with [web.stanford.edu/~rjohari/ Ramesh Johari ] and [https://profiles.stanford.edu/blanchet Jose Blanchet]. 

Prior to this, I am Postdoctoral Researcher at [http://www.msr-inria.fr Microsoft Research - Inria Joint center], hosted by [http://www.msr-inria.fr/researchers/laurent-massoulie/ Dr. Laurent Massoulie], [http://www.di.ens.fr/~lelarge/ Dr. Marc Lelarge], and [http://research.microsoft.com/en-us/people/milanv/ Dr. Milan Vojnovic], from Jan 2016 to July 2017.

Before that, I was Simons Postdoctoral Fellow at [http://www.utexas.edu/ The University of Texas at Austin] hosted by [http://www.ma.utexas.edu/users/baccelli/ Prof. Francois Baccelli] in Fall of 2015.

I obtained my PhD at [http://www.utexas.edu/ The University of Texas at Austin] in August 2015 under supervision of [http://users.ece.utexas.edu/~gustavo/ Prof. Gustavo de Veciana]. 

I have also held research positions at [https://www.bell-labs.com/ Bell Labs] New Jersey, [http://www.iitb.ac.in/ Indian Institute of Technology (IIT) Bombay], and [http://www.iisc.ac.in/ Indian Institute of Science (IISc) Bangalore].

== Research Summary 

- Design online matching markets
- Machine learning applications
